# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Private layer — operator's clone of the private companion repo.
# CRITICAL: this directory is private operational state. Anything
# accidentally added here would leak when the public twin is pushed.
.private/

# Twin signing key — the on-device twin's PRIVATE Ed25519 half.
# CRITICAL: this is the sealed substance that NEVER travels in the bones.
# Only the public half (keys/twin.pub + card.json twin.pubkey) is published.
keys/twin.key
keys/*.key

# Estate key shards (§15) — Shamir splits of the private key + their printable QR SVGs.
# CRITICAL: any k of these reconstruct the twin. They are printed and distributed BY HAND
# (safe, will, trusted heir) — never committed, never networked. The whole dir is sealed.
keys/shards/

# Brainstem state — runtime, not source
.brainstem_data/
.copilot_token
.copilot_session
.copilot_pending
.brainstem_book.json
voice.zip

